docker run -d -v alarmservice_data_volume:/var/lib/mysql --name alarmservice_data_container mariadb:latest

OBS! STATUS OF LINES BELOW IS UNCLEAR!!

To create a new image locally, tagged "infinera/mariadb-data-image", run
docker build -t mariadb-data-image .

To create a data-only container, named "mariadb-data-container", run
docker create --name mariadb-data-container mariadb-data-image
